{"tid":449011,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］放低你地最深刻既遊戲user name","createTime":"2017-10-26T18:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T08:57:04.000Z","uid":44747,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"090a25b89a44a3a45aa505c8e3a37c109ce712b5","tid":449011,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"果陣玩ceo識左條友，初頭同佢都會一齊做下任升下lv，最記得就係憑依佢身上去遺跡之塔升lv。<br />\n不過果陣佢中六我中一，佢本身係澳門人就話去台灣讀大學。仲記得佢果陣用電話線成日都好慢又lag咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過你去左台灣之後就少左玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你仲留左個email比我add你msn，果陣又冇msn。<br />\n到有果陣因爲個server合併左，就冇哂啲record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左九年後的依家，一齊都想搵返你同你講聲我過得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保護的Jimmy呢個名我會記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係玉屋清吉呀（如果你仲記得的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n仲有會長同會長夫人，希望你地都依家都仲一齊，美滿幸福咁生活落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到依家隻game執左都好，啲回憶仲會係度抹唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff378f1b13690557e58d5478b63e28d61aa6054","tid":449011,"uid":44747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"Eco至岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70f611da37f0662663f1534f345f9546abe1cac","tid":449011,"uid":94025,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T19:04:31.000Z","msg":"以前小五六玩跑online 識左個女仔 遊戲名已經唔記得 真名叫x雪瑩 住慈雲山 記得果陣日日都傾電話一齊玩 過左一兩年 冇再聯絡 點知有一日search自己個真名 無意間見到佢個blog 之後留cm 果陣再交換番電話 可惜都係傾左一次半次之後就冇聯絡 好記得果陣仲話等我上左中一 要搵次約出黎玩 好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fa1e87ba4a84a30aefa263c738ee5db6090af5"